     [ID badge] EventType · primary (+ chip) — meta / "secondary".
     Badges mirror the Data Catalog commitment-ID badge idiom (compact mono/
     semibold tinted token): observation IDs = the page's --obs-color violet,
     work-area IDs = primary-teal tint (deliberately NOT a second violet — the
     page's whole grammar keeps work areas and observations distinct). ═══ */
  :global(.entry) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--spacing-300);
    padding: var(--spacing-250) var(--spacing-300);
  }
  :global(.entry__badge) {
